cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is about text mining and natural language processing, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of vector representations and topic models, which are common in machine learning and data mining, falling under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the optimization of these models, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
